【Solution】Solution: $(3+0.5):(3-0.5)=7: 5$,
$$
\begin{array}{l}
3 \times(7+5) \div 5 \\
=7.2 \text { (hours) }
\end{array}
$$

Answer: B needs 7.2 hours to travel from A to B.
The answer is: 7.2.

